actions.message:
```
GENERAL-----------
Help                          Give you this
RequestRoom                   If you want a temporary room use this
Fired                         It will fire anyone... and I mean **ANYONE**
Blacklisted                   All words that have been blacklisted

MUSIC COMMANDS -----------
Play                          Play a song off of a YouTube URL
Leave                         Forces the Bot to leave the voice channel
Pause                         Pauses the current song
Resume                        Resumes the current song
Volume                        Adjust the bots volume
Stop                          Stops all music from playing
Skip                          Skips the current song

ADMIN ONLY -----------
CheckID                       Enter a string of numbers you believe is related to a user and it spits out the user's tag.
TTS                           Make the bot use text to speech (Requires the ability to ban people)
Blacklist                     This command does not work right now
Clear                         Clears the chat of a set amount of messages
Ban                           Mention a user to ban someone
```

**.requestroom <minutes> <room name> <members allowed to join>**

Room names **MUST** be one word, if you need it to be more please use underscores.
If you want any number of people to join please put the third parameter to 100.
